				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-30/poem-xwsqwPKt0MMZLZooPcmZkw">Cảm ngộ kỳ 30 - 感遇其三十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/Canh-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-tri-ph%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BB%AFu-ty-Mai-Phong-L%C3%AA-c%C3%B4ng-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-KAZCEsdik3KWy-ELUrNEOA">Canh đồng tri phủ hữu ty Mai Phong Lê công vận - 賡同知府右司梅峰黎公韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/H%C3%A1n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mSH9PE5CreDWAB83y1xujw">Hán tướng hành - 漢將行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-RNpImmo2Zi_8n8IJeKR5eg">Thẩm Đức Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87/L%C5%A9ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A7u-ng%C3%A2m/poem-DcrNd3xJDkMcaL1Tx2C6sQ">Lũng Đầu ngâm - 隴頭吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87/author-PjzIG1r2C2XpMeVwfYjbJw">Tiết Huệ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Quan-h%E1%BA%A3i/poem-o8HaXeEyR21CIUGTUVs8_A">Quan hải - 關海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-di-ch%E1%BB%A9c-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-NJvolbIcDjypA5I_hCVmCw">Thái tử Trương xá nhân di chức thành nhục đoạn - 太子張舍人遺織成褥段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/Thung-L%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-p2nhZFT0UlZaSH48t6Kosw">Thung Lăng hành - 舂陵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/author-9Y30zD24BFXrRqipoBvcFA">Nguyên Kết</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/%E1%BB%B6-Lan-nguy%C3%AAn-phi/poem-GClzVsbYCFlOmj8rwqUdXw">Ỷ Lan nguyên phi - 椅蘭元妃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br></div>	</div>
